# ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  x11forward - X11 SSH Forwarding Utility                 ║
# ║  Automates dependency checks, remote configuration,      ║
# ║  and establishes X11-forwarded SSH sessions.              ║
